---
import VantageLayout from '../../../layouts/VantageLayout.astro';
import { gameplan, brand } from '../../../data/vantage';
---

<VantageLayout title="How It Works — VANTAGE Men's Health" description="The VANTAGE Game Plan — from assessment to optimization. Lab-based, provider-guided, and personalized.">

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<section class="vt-s vt-s--black hiw-hero">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<span class="vt-e">The VANTAGE Game Plan</span>
		<h1>From assessment<br/>to optimization.</h1>
		<p class="vt-sub">No guesswork. No rushed appointments. A structured process built for clarity — from first assessment to ongoing performance tracking.</p>
		<div class="vt-btn-row" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--red" href="/demos/hormone-trt/assessment">Start My Assessment &rarr;</a>
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--dark" href="/demos/hormone-trt/book-consultation">Book a Private Consult</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ 6-STEP GAME PLAN — field-line steps on bone ═══ -->
<section class="vt-s vt-s--bone hiw-gp">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<span class="vt-e">The Process</span>
		<h2>Six steps. One clear path forward.</h2>
		<p class="vt-sub">Every patient follows this framework — adapted to their specific symptoms, goals, and lab results.</p>
		<div class="hiw-field">
			<div class="hiw-field__line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
			{gameplan.map((s, i) => (
				<div class:list={['hiw-field__step', { 'hiw-field__step--first': i === 0 }]}>
					<span class="hiw-field__marker">{s.step}</span>
					<span class="hiw-field__label">{s.label}</span>
					<p class="hiw-field__desc">{s.description}</p>
				</div>
			))}
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ EXPANDED STEP DETAILS ═══ -->
<section class="vt-s vt-s--charcoal hiw-detail-sec">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<span class="vt-e">Step-by-Step</span>
		<h2>What happens at each stage.</h2>
		<div class="hiw-detail">
			<div class="hiw-detail__item">
				<div class="hiw-detail__head">
					<span class="hiw-detail__num">01</span>
					<h3>Assessment</h3>
				</div>
				<p>A private, 2-minute online questionnaire covering your primary symptoms, health history, lifestyle, and goals. This information helps your provider prepare for a focused consultation.</p>
				<p>No medical records are required upfront. You can complete the assessment from any device at any time.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-detail__item">
				<div class="hiw-detail__head">
					<span class="hiw-detail__num">02</span>
					<h3>Labs</h3>
				</div>
				<p>Your provider orders a comprehensive panel based on your assessment responses. Labs can be completed at a local Quest or Labcorp location, or at our clinic.</p>
				<p>Panels typically include: Total & Free Testosterone, SHBG, Estradiol, DHEA-S, PSA, CBC, CMP, Thyroid, Lipids, HbA1c, Vitamin D, and inflammatory markers.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-detail__item">
				<div class="hiw-detail__head">
					<span class="hiw-detail__num">03</span>
					<h3>Provider Review</h3>
				</div>
				<p>A private 45–60 minute consultation (in-person or telehealth) to review your lab results in detail. Your provider explains what each marker means, how they relate to your symptoms, and what options exist.</p>
				<p>This is a conversation, not a sales pitch. You'll leave with clarity — whether or not treatment is recommended.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-detail__item">
				<div class="hiw-detail__head">
					<span class="hiw-detail__num">04</span>
					<h3>Treatment Plan</h3>
				</div>
				<p>If treatment is clinically appropriate, your provider builds a personalized protocol. This may include hormone optimization, medications, peptides, or lifestyle recommendations — all grounded in your specific data.</p>
				<p>You review the plan together, ask questions, and decide how to proceed. Nothing begins without your informed consent.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-detail__item">
				<div class="hiw-detail__head">
					<span class="hiw-detail__num">05</span>
					<h3>Follow-Up</h3>
				</div>
				<p>Regular check-ins ensure your protocol is working as expected. Your provider reviews symptoms, adjusts dosing, and addresses any concerns in follow-up visits — in-person or via telehealth.</p>
				<p>Provider messaging and priority scheduling keep you connected between visits.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-detail__item hiw-detail__item--last">
				<div class="hiw-detail__head">
					<span class="hiw-detail__num">06</span>
					<h3>Optimization</h3>
				</div>
				<p>Treatment is not a one-time event. Your provider monitors your labs quarterly, adjusts protocols based on your response, and ensures your care stays on track over time.</p>
				<p>The goal is ongoing improvement — not just a number on a chart, but how you actually feel and perform.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ WHAT MAKES VANTAGE DIFFERENT ═══ -->
<section class="vt-s vt-s--black hiw-diff-sec">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<span class="vt-e">The Difference</span>
		<h2>What makes VANTAGE different.</h2>
		<div class="hiw-diff">
			<div class="hiw-diff__item">
				<span class="hiw-diff__dot"></span>
				<div>
					<h3>Lab-first approach</h3>
					<p>We never prescribe without testing first. Every protocol is grounded in your actual biomarker data — not assumptions or symptom checklists alone.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-diff__item">
				<span class="hiw-diff__dot"></span>
				<div>
					<h3>Licensed providers only</h3>
					<p>Your care is managed by board-certified physicians and experienced PAs specializing in men's health and hormone medicine.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-diff__item">
				<span class="hiw-diff__dot"></span>
				<div>
					<h3>No pressure, no upselling</h3>
					<p>If treatment isn't appropriate for you, we'll tell you. Our goal is appropriate care — not maximum revenue per patient.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-diff__item">
				<span class="hiw-diff__dot"></span>
				<div>
					<h3>Ongoing relationship</h3>
					<p>This isn't a transactional prescription service. We build lasting provider-patient relationships with regular check-ins and accessible communication.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-diff__item">
				<span class="hiw-diff__dot"></span>
				<div>
					<h3>Privacy & discretion</h3>
					<p>Sexual health, hormone therapy, and weight management are treated with the same discretion and professionalism as any other medical specialty.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hiw-diff__item hiw-diff__item--last">
				<span class="hiw-diff__dot"></span>
				<div>
					<h3>Transparent pricing</h3>
					<p>You'll know what things cost before you commit. No surprise bills, hidden fees, or bundled services you didn't ask for.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ CTA — RED PANEL ═══ -->
<section class="hiw-final">
	<div class="vt-w hiw-final__inner">
		<span class="vt-e">Decision Time</span>
		<h2>Ready to build your plan?</h2>
		<p class="vt-sub">Start with a private assessment — it takes less than 2 minutes. Your provider will review your responses and guide the next step.</p>
		<div class="vt-btn-row" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--red" href="/demos/hormone-trt/assessment" style="background:var(--vt-white);color:var(--vt-red);border-color:var(--vt-white);">Start My Assessment &rarr;</a>
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--dark" href="/demos/hormone-trt/book-consultation" style="background:transparent;color:var(--vt-white);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">Book a Private Consult</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ DISCLAIMER ═══ -->
<div class="vt-s--black" style="padding:0 0 2rem;">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<p class="hiw-disc">{brand.disclaimer}</p>
	</div>
</div>

</VantageLayout>

<style>
/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   HOW IT WORKS — Elite Sports Performance Medicine
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

/* Hero */
.hiw-hero { padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.hiw-hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -40%; right: -10%; width: 45%; height: 180%; background: var(--vt-red); transform: skewX(-12deg); opacity: 0.04; pointer-events: none; }
.hiw-hero h1 { max-width: 600px; }
.hiw-hero .vt-sub { max-width: 500px; }

/* 6-step game plan — field-line steps on bone */
.hiw-gp h2 { max-width: 400px; }
.hiw-gp .vt-sub { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
.hiw-field { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr); gap: 0; position: relative; }
.hiw-field__line { position: absolute; top: 1.15rem; left: 1.5rem; right: 1.5rem; height: 2px; background: var(--vt-border-light); z-index: 0; }
.hiw-field__step { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; }
.hiw-field__marker { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 2.3rem; height: 2.3rem; margin: 0 auto 0.75rem; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--vt-white); background: var(--vt-charcoal); border: 2px solid var(--vt-charcoal); border-radius: 50%; }
.hiw-field__step--first .hiw-field__marker { background: var(--vt-red); border-color: var(--vt-red); }
.hiw-field__label { display: block; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--vt-black); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.hiw-field__desc { font-size: 0.62rem; color: var(--vt-steel); line-height: 1.4; padding: 0 0.25rem; }

/* Expanded step details */
.hiw-detail-sec h2 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.hiw-detail { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; max-width: 700px; }
.hiw-detail__item { padding: 1.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vt-border); }
.hiw-detail__item--last { border-bottom: none; }
.hiw-detail__head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
.hiw-detail__num { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--vt-red); line-height: 1; min-width: 1.5rem; }
.hiw-detail__item h3 { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0; }
.hiw-detail__item p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.5); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

/* What makes VANTAGE different — stacked rows with red accent dots */
.hiw-diff-sec h2 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.hiw-diff { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; max-width: 700px; }
.hiw-diff__item { display: flex; gap: 0.85rem; padding: 1.2rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vt-border); align-items: start; }
.hiw-diff__item--last { border-bottom: none; }
.hiw-diff__dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; min-width: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--vt-red); margin-top: 0.35rem; }
.hiw-diff__item h3 { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.hiw-diff__item p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.5); line-height: 1.55; }

/* CTA — red panel */
.hiw-final { background: var(--vt-red); padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.hiw-final::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -30%; right: -5%; width: 40%; height: 160%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.08); transform: skewX(-12deg); pointer-events: none; }
.hiw-final__inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.hiw-final h2 { color: var(--vt-white); }
.hiw-final .vt-e { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
.hiw-final .vt-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

/* Disclaimer */
.hiw-disc { font-size: 0.55rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.12); font-style: italic; max-width: 560px; }

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
	.hiw-field { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem 0; }
	.hiw-field__line { display: none; }
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
	.hiw-field { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
</style>
